<h3>Accent Buttons</h3>
<p>Accent buttons are to be used where there are multiple buttons on the screen and we want to call attention to the most important action on the screen. Only one accent button should be visible on the screen at a time.</p>
<div class="button-row">
  <div class="button-grid">
    <button type="submit" href="#" class="button button_accent">{{ btnText }}</button>
    <div class="button-label">State: Default</div>
  </div>
  <div class="button-grid">
    <button type="submit" href="#" class="button button_accent hover">{{ btnText }}</button>
    <div class="button-label">State: Hover</div>
  </div>
  <div class="button-grid">
    <button type="submit" href="#" class="button button_accent pressed">{{ btnText }}</button>
    <div class="button-label">State: Pressed</div>
  </div>
</div>
